reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for the Stanley x Swiftie girls!
reviews.reviewText: This name plate is the perfect Stanley accessory for the Taylor Swift fan in your life. I bought this for my daughter and she absolutely loved it! She tried to put it on her 30oz, but it didn't fit so I went back and read the description and realized it was for a 40oz. Luckily she has both, but definitely read before you buy! Other than my small mistake she loves the name plate and it fits on her 40oz cup perfectly!
